@node "Introduction" "Introduction"

                       @{b}@{u}Introduction@{ub}@{uu}


I wasn't satisfied of the currently available message saving scripts so I've
wrote mine and I've wrote it to allow use from both Thor's ARexx menu and
from another script.
@endnode

@node "Thor" "Using with Thor"

            @{b}@{u}Using GMarchive from Thor@{ub}@{uu}


This script can be used either from Thor's @{i}ARexx script@{ui} menu or from another
script (as I've done with mine @{"GMCleanConf.thor" link "GMCleanConf.guide/main" 0})

 Parameters:

   @{b}<none>@{ub}    to save the currently selected msg (useful as an ARexx menu
               script)

     or

   @{b}BBSNAME/A CONFNAME/A MSGNUM/A/N ARCFILE EXTRACOMM/S@{ub}

   @{b}BBSNAME@{ub}   This is the System name, required
   @{b}CONFNAME@{ub}  This is the Conference name, required
   @{b}MSGNUM@{ub}    This is the Message Number, required
   @{b}ARCFILE@{ub}   This is the fully qualified file, default is THOR's Save dir
               plus 'GM' plus first_14_chars_of_subject plus '.txt'
               if there is no subject name is 'GMarchivedMsgs.txt'
               If file already exists the message is appended
   @{b}EXTRACOMM@{ub} Switch to save *all* the message's comments, default to save
               only the basic ones
@endnode

@node "Distribution" "Distribution "

            @{b}@{u}Distribution@{ub}@{uu}

GMarchive.thor is freely distributable, but remains (c) Gian Maria Calzolari,
1999.

It may not be distribuited alone but only with the @{"GMsuite" link "GMsuite.guide/distribution" 0} archive.
@endnode

@node "History" "History"

            @{b}@{u}History@{ub}@{uu}


@{i}07 Jan 2000@{ui} : @{b}5.2@{ub} : Used ReadArguments in GMsignature to avoid errors when
                    crossposting news

@{i}21 Dec 1999@{ui} : @{b}5.1@{ub} : Nothing, bumped up rev

@{i}17 Nov 1999@{ui} : @{b}5.0@{ub} : Bumped up rev for consinstency with first aminet
                    release of GMsuite!
                    Added flags 'Marked' and 'SuperMarked' but they mean
                    'Unread' and 'SuperUnread'!

@{i}16 Nov 1999@{ui} : @{b}2.4@{ub} : tried to add flag 'UnRead' but it doesn't work!

@{i}15 Nov 1999@{ui} : @{b}2.3@{ub} : Msg flags are now correctly printed for the 'main' msg
                    only

@{i}14 Nov 1999@{ui} : @{b}2.2@{ub} : changed the way parms are checked to allow use from Thor
                    Rexx menu and changed the default filename

@{i}08 Nov 1999@{ui} : @{b}2.1@{ub} : ExtraComments is now a parameter

@{i}07 Nov 1999@{ui} : @{b}2.0@{ub} : First working version! :-))

@{i}31 Oct 1999@{ui} : @{b}1.4@{ub} : Thor conversion started...

@{i}10 Jan 1999@{ui} : @{b}1.3@{ub} : Last EMS version
@endnode

